target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000010_RYNE<tab>Le Primordial va apparaître... Bonne chance<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000030_RYNE<tab>It worked! Both wind and fire have answered the call!

target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000040_GAIA<tab>Ryne<var 1D /var>! Ça va, tu tiens le coup<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000050_RYNE<tab>So many of them... But nothing we can't handle!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000050_RYNE<tab>Ils sont si nombreux... Faites très attention à vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000060_RYNE<tab>I call...upon the power of Shiva!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000060_RYNE<tab>Je suis prête à recevoir le pouvoir de Shiva<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000080_GAIA<tab>No! She's lost control! You've got to stop her!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05201_000080_GAIA<tab>C'est en train de partir en vrille<var 1D /var>! Faut l'arrêter, et tout de suite<var 1D /var>!
